.s-rule.consider
  :marked
    **Consider** spelling `const` variables in lower camel case.

    **考虑** 把常量名拼写为小驼峰格式。

.s-why
  :marked
    **Why?** Lower camel case variable names (`heroRoutes`) are easier to read and understand
    than the traditional UPPER_SNAKE_CASE names (`HERO_ROUTES`).

